<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="6Jun1938"><font color="red">6 June 1938</font> <i>NLGC</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to National Geographic Society) Your subscriber Mrs James Joyce asks me to write &hellip; Has there been published in any of your issues in the past years (recently) an article on the life of the natives in the Bismarck Archipelago and in the Solomon Islands? </div>
